I don't know much about this guy, Moyseis Marques. This one seems to be his debut album, but he sounds so assured - his singing and also the musicians around him - that it sounds like a classic Samba album. Yes, this is about Samba. Not the street Carnival way, this is a super-relaxed affair, arranged in a timeless manner.
This is the auspicious beginning of a promising career. Thumbs up! Good luck, Moyseis!
